										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Nabel株式會社 在 JIMTOF 2022 處展示了 “TM ROBOT”和“Robot-Flex”。</p>
<p>網站：<a href="https://www.bellows.co.jp/ja/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.bellows.co.jp/ja/</a></p>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-1.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">這個TM機器人叫Techman Robot。<br />有兩個特點，它是世界上第一個內置攝像頭的機器人。</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-2.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">另一個優點是易於編程。</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-3.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">像這樣，它的特點是可以像流程圖一樣方便地編程。</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-4.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">通過安裝相機，重要的是能夠通過識別此處的定位地標立即在該位置執行相同的操作，</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-5.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">即使位置發生變化。</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-6.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">這是附在機器人上的，這是機器人的外殼。</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-7.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">我們是一家波紋管製造商，所以我們擅長材料開發，而機器人經常在各種環境中使用，所以我們有</div>
</div>
<div class="caption_box">
<div class="caption_img"><img decoding="async" src="https://www.tenji.tv/wp-content/uploads/video_img/jimtof_2022_11/jimtof_2022_11_03-8.jpg"></div>
<div class="caption_text">6種材料變化的陣容。 </div>
</div>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="/contents/43150/">[JIMTOF 2022] “TM ROBOT”和“Robot-Flex” - Nabel株式會社</a> 最早出現於 <a href="/">在線觀看展覽！WorldTradeShow.tv | 繁體中文</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
